Package: flode
Title: Forecasting Operations and Development Environment
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Forecasting and Warning Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "forecasting@environment-agency.gov.uk")
Description: Flode is the Forecasting and Warning team's meta-package.
    Loading flode attaches all core sub-packages (reach.io, reach.hydro,
    reach.ensemble, reach.validate, reach.viz, reach.utils) and prints a
    startup message confirming what was loaded. Modelled on the tidyverse
    meta-package pattern.
